{{Quote|I had never seen anything like it. The Mon Calamari vessel was huge. Our tiny shuttle floated next to it like a bitz bug next to a bantha.|[[Keyan Farlander/Legends|Keyan Farlander]]|<ref name="X-Wing: The Official Strategy Guide">''[[X-Wing: The Official Strategy Guide]]''</ref>}}
'''Bitz bugs''' were tiny insects found on several planets. There were several varieties and they were frequently found to be annoying. Bitz bugs could be found on the planet [[Agamar/Legends|Agamar]].

